7. Give your reasoning on which is the best model in this case and why it performs better?

KNN has the best accuracy(95.93 %) and less False Positive and False Negative as compare to other Models.
But KNN is slower and requires more storage as compare to other models.
If accuracy is concern Logistic Regression and KNN doesn't have any prominent difference.
So i think Logistic Regression would be best fit
